snippet.title: OFF DUTY Trailer
snippet.description:
Off_Duty is an FPS game that takes place in an Indian city. The protagonist is an off duty special agent who is trying to investigate an illegal operation in an older area of the city. He must face overwhelming odds.

Download Link:
